reviewText: Not in the condition it said it was dvd scratched and the case broken label cover ripped apart not happy!! Not new condition!
Love this video content from BabyFirst TV channel and I buy it for my son's continual development.
Raised my daughter on this and she loved it.  Now I got this for my son and he loves it too.
My son loves the series, it's way better than Sesame Street.  The only thing I wish I would have known is that the video is only 45 mins long.  I already know my son is going to get board.
Thank you BabyFirstTV for adding your programs to DVD. My niece LOVES the programs and having them on DVD makes life so much easier.
